code: @Override public String toString() {     if (pdu != null) {         return "SnmpMessage: " + SnmpConverters.toString(pdu).     } else {         return "SnmpMessage: " + getBody().     } }
/**  * Returns the underlying SNMP message  */ public PDU getSnmpMessage() {     return this.pdu. }
@Override public SnmpMessage newInstance() {     return new SnmpMessage(getCamelContext(), this.pdu). }
